DK-NA: 2.
   5. How many people will you be giving Christmas gifts to this
year? None: 3. One-two: 2. Three-five: 8. Six-nine: 16. Ten-14: 28.
Fifteen-20: 21. Twenty-plus: 20. DK-NA: 3.
